Package: CalorICU
Type: Package
Title: CalorICU is a set of tools to analize the Urban Heat Island 
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    c(person(given = "Omar",
             family = "Barrantes-Sotela",
             role = c("aut", "cre"),
             email = "omar.barrantes.sotela@una.ac.cr",
             comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-4225-5784"))
             )
Maintainer: The package maintainer <omar.barrantes.sotela@una.ac.cr>
Description: Toolset for study the Urban Heat Island phenomena in a city o urban environment.
    Use meteorological dataset from meteorological station on the ground to calibrate the termal band of sensors like
    Landsat 5, Landsat 7 and Landsat 9 to get superficial temperature of the ground.
    A fast, consistent tool for working with data frame
    like objects, both in memory and out of memory.
